{"id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0002","text":"此刻的歌聲 不可以暫停 叫愛的感覺 能得到見證","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","表達","見證"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["歌聲","暫停","愛","感覺","見證"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,3,3,3,3,9,5,2,0,4,4,3,9,4,0,3,4,4,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ci2","hak1","dik1","go1","sing1","bat1","ho2","ji5","zaam6","ting4","giu3","oi3","dik1","gam2","gok3","nang4","dak1","dou3","gin3","zing3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"此刻","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"歌聲","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可以","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"暫停","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"感覺","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"得到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"見證","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「不可以暫停」的歌聲，對比上一行的「暫停」，強調愛的表達不能停止。"},"source":{"title":"天真","artists":["杜德偉"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","R&B"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1327","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0003","text":"原來柔情亦會彼此感染 從來柔情就似天地自然","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","感染","自然"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["柔情","感染","天地","自然"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,0,0,2,9,9,9,5,0,0,0,0,2,5,3,2,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyun4","loi4","jau4","cing4","jik6","bei2","ci2","gam2","jim5","cung4","loi4","jau4","cing4","zau6","ci5","tin1","dei6","zi6","jin4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"原來","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"柔情","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"彼此","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"感染","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"從來","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"柔情","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"似","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天地","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"自然","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"使用「原來」和「從來」連接兩個分句，強調柔情如同天地自然般，是互相感染且理所當然的。"},"source":{"title":"天真","artists":["杜德偉"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","R&B"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1327","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0004","text":"絕管不了這是誰人的差遣 熱戀眼睛 全被愛遮掩","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","盲目","遮掩"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["管不了","差遣","熱戀","眼睛","遮掩"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,9,3,5,5,2,0,0,3,3,9,2,9,5,3,0,2,4,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zyut6","gun2","bat1","liu5","ze5","si6","seoi4","jan4","dik1","caa1","hin2","jit6","lyun2","ngaan5","zing1","cyun4","bei6","oi3","ze1","jim2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"絕","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"管不了","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"差遣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"熱戀","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"眼睛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"全","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"被","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"遮掩","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「絕管不了」表示無法控制，強調熱戀中的盲目，連眼睛都被愛意所遮蔽。"},"source":{"title":"天真","artists":["杜德偉"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","R&B"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1327","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0005","text":"我這個愛人 有點天真 但天生懂得去 來引你開心","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","天真","取悅"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["愛人","天真","懂得","開心"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,4,4,0,5,9,3,3,2,3,3,9,3,4,0,5,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","ze5","go3","oi3","jan4","jau5","dim2","tin1","zan1","daan6","tin1","sang1","dung2","dak1","heoi3","loi4","jan5","nei5","hoi1","sam1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"愛人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"有點","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"天真","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"天生","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"懂得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"去","pos":"PART"},{"text":"來","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"引","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"開心","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「有點天真」和「但天生懂得去來引你開心」形成對比，描繪出愛人天真卻又懂得如何讓對方快樂的特質。"},"source":{"title":"天真","artists":["杜德偉"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","R&B"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1327","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0006","text":"我愛你眼神 愛得天真 什麼都不知道 惟用心去吻","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","天真","純粹"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["眼神","天真","知道","用心","吻"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,5,5,0,4,3,3,3,2,3,3,3,3,2,0,2,3,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","oi3","nei5","ngaan5","san4","oi3","dak1","tin1","zan1","sam6","mo1","dou1","bat1","zi1","dou6","wai4","jung6","sam1","heoi3","man5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我愛你","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"眼神","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"愛得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天真","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"知道","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"惟","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"用心","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"去","pos":"PART"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「愛得天真」呼應上一行，並以「什麼都不知道」強調愛的純粹，只憑藉「用心去吻」來表達。"},"source":{"title":"天真","artists":["杜德偉"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","R&B"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1327","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
