{"id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0008","text":"杯中的清水 應該似蜜甜 似你那張臉 從不會看厭","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","美好","滿足"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["清水","蜜甜","臉","看厭"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,3,9,3,5,2,0,5,5,5,3,5,0,3,4,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bui1","zung1","dik1","cing1","seoi2","goi1","ci5","mat6","tim4","ci5","nei5","naa5","zoeng1","lim5","cung4","bat1","hon3","jim3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"杯中","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"清水","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"應該","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"似","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"蜜甜","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"似","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"那","pos":"DET"},{"text":"張臉","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"從","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"不會","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"看厭","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"將清水比喻為蜜甜，並與愛人的臉龐連結，表達了對愛人美好形象的讚賞與永不厭倦的喜愛。"},"source":{"title":"天真","artists":["杜德偉"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","R&B"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1327","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2c5b635Lyf_MTMyNw_0007","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
